Read ARIADNE Reference Scenario

Source: R/readARIADNE.R
readARIADNE_ReferenceScenario.Rd

Alias to readARIADNE. May be deprecated in the future.

readARIADNE_ReferenceScenario(subtype)

Arguments

subtype

data subtype. Either "population", "gdp", or "gdp_corona"

Value

magpie object of ARIADNE reference scenario data by country

See also

madrat::readSource()
